     "Print", "[", "\"\<We solve Case a again, but with the extra condition \
that A(t,r)=\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(c\), \(2\)]\). It is possible we may \
obtain a different solution by setting A(t,r)=\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(c\), \(2\
\)]\) \!\(\*StyleBox[\"before\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\) trying to solve the \
ODEs.\>\"", "]"}], ";", "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
