"\"\<\!\(\*StyleBox[\"c\",FontWeight->\"Bold\",FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, \
1]]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\"-\",FontWeight->\"Bold\",FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, \
1]]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\"II\",FontWeight->\"Bold\",FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 1]]\
\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\":\",FontWeight->\"Bold\",FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 1]]\)\!\
\(\*StyleBox[\"  \",FontWeight->\"Bold\",FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, \
